text: Heliophanus montanus is a jumping spider species in the genus Heliophanus. It was first described by Wanda Wesołowska in 2006 in Namibia. ==References== Category:Salticidae Category:Fauna of Namibia Category:Spiders of Africa Category:Spiders described in 2006 Category:Taxa named by Wanda Wesołowska
title: Heliophanus montanus
